overview.en: Using block chain technology to construct a de-centralized shopping platform, GFC will be one of the important passes in the platform. Perfect community concept and simple shopping process will bring users extraordinary experience.
overview.zh: 利用区块链技术 构建去中心化购物平台 GFC将是平台中重要通证之一 完善的社区理念 简单的购物流程 将会给用户带来非凡的体验。
